title: Time Tenshi Paradox: Episode 1
description: History hangs in the balance...The Time Tenshi narrowly saved the future, but what lurks in the past?Join Rose, Kyo, Tessa and Michelle in the first episode of Time Tenshi Paradox, a new episodic visual novel series from Silver Cow Studio!Thanks to your grandfather's secret invention, a machine known as the Time Window, mankind's grandest dream - to travel through time - is now a reality!
